1. *Javi* kad budeš stigao kući. (Let me know when you get home.)
2. Ukoliko nešto ne bude u redu, *javiću* ti odmah. (If something goes wrong, I'll let you know immediately.)
3. Nisam još siguran da li ću moći da dođem, *javiću* ti sutra. (I'm not sure yet if I'll be able to come, I'll let you know tomorrow.)
4. Kada sam se probudio, *javi* da mi doneseš kafu. (When I wake up, let me know to bring me coffee.)
5. *Javiću* se u vezi ovog posla u toku dana. (I will get in touch regarding this job during the day.)
6. Ne brini, *javiću* ti kada budem na putu. (Don't worry, I will let you know when I'm on my way.)
7. *Javi* ako ti nešto treba. (Let me know if you need anything.)
8. Molim te, *javi* mi da li si stigao na aerodrom. (Please let me know if you arrived at the airport.)
9. Moram da *javim* roditeljima da kasnim na ručak. (I have to tell my parents that I'm running late for lunch.)
10. Kada završiš posao, *javi mi* da te sačekam ispred kancelarije. (When you finish your work, let me know so I can wait for you in front of the office.)